data.description: With its prime location in the heart of Locust Grove, the spacious and open floor plan creates an inviting atmosphere for both entertaining guests and enjoying quality time with loved ones. The primary suite provides amenities like a walk-in closet, separate soaking tub, and dual vanity. Additionally, the large bonus room upstairs with a half bath provides versatility, allowing residents to customize the space to suit their needs! Moreover, the property's proximity to various amenities such as shopping centers, restaurants, parks, schools, and more enhances its appeal, promising residents' easy access to everything Locust Grove has to offer. Ask how you can receive up to $500 credit by using one of our preferred lenders. Exclusions may apply.
